---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/main.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About Corey Burns" description="A quick look at Corey Burns and the work behind the blog.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-12 py-12 pb-24 text-white">
    <header class="mb-16 gc-fade">
      <p class="text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/40">~/about.md</p>
      <h1 class="mt-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter" data-text="DESIGNING WITH INTENTION">
        DESIGNING WITH INTENTION, <br/><span class="text-white/40">SHIPPING WITH SPEED.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/50 border-l-2 border-[#00ff88] pl-4">
        I’m Corey Burns, a full-stack product designer and engineer. I partner with teams to translate ambitious ideas into
        performant, human-centered experiences.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
      <div class="gc-entry border border-white/5 bg-white/1 p-8 md:p-12 article-content hover:border-white/10 transition-colors" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <p>
          My work blends design systems, frontend engineering, and rapid experimentation. I’m obsessed with crafting tools
          and interfaces that feel inevitable—simple, fast, and memorable.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I’m not building, I’m documenting processes, refining workflows, and exploring the future of creative AI.
        </p>
      </div>
      <aside class="gc-entry border border-white/5 bg-white/1 p-8 md:p-12 hover:border-white/10 transition-colors" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <h2 class="text-xl uppercase font-bold text-white/80">Capabilities</h2>
        <ul class="mt-8 grid gap-4 text-xs font-mono text-white/60">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#00ff88]">[x]</span>
            Product strategy + UX systems
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#00ff88]">[x]</span>
            Frontend engineering + performance
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#00ff88]">[x]</span>
            AI-powered design tooling
          </li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
